Which HTTP method would you use to update a record through an API? ~You would use a PUT or PATCH technique to update a record.
Which REST methods require an ID parameter? ~the HEAD method, GET method, PUT method, PATCH method, and DELETE method.

Whatâ€™s the relationship between REST and CRUD? ~RESTful APIs structure their endpoints in a way that maps HTTP methods to CRUD processes, which is how REST and CRUD are related.
